---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Private Special Class | Private Karate Lessons"
  description="Private and small-group instruction at the Seishinkai Headquarters Dojo in Sapporo. Our Private Special Class offers one-on-one or small-group lessons scheduled at times convenient for you."
  lang="en"
  path="/en/dojo/kobetsu/"
>
  <section class="dojo-list">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="section__title-area">
        <span class="section-label">PRIVATE LESSONS</span>
        <h1 class="section-title">Sapporo Karate Dojo — Private Special Class</h1>
      </div>

      <p class="detail-page__lead">
        [Sapporo Karate Classes / Private & Small-Group Instruction]<br />
        Outside our regular practice days, we offer one-on-one or small-group lessons tailored to the individual, scheduled to fit your personal availability.<br />
        Both Headquarters and branch members are welcome to take these lessons, and it is also possible to join from the start as a private-instruction-only member rather than through the regular course.<br />
        Content ranges from basics, kata, and applications (bunkai) at beginner through advanced levels, and can also be tailored to a health-focused course or a self-defense-focused course depending on your goals.
      </p>

      <div class="detail-gallery">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/kobetsu/img6.jpg"
            alt="A private lesson in progress"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>Private Instruction</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/legacy/dojo/kobetsu/img2.jpg"
            alt="A small-group lesson in progress"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <figcaption>Small-Group Instruction</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <p>
        Lesson dates and times are arranged in advance by mutual agreement.<br />
        We can accommodate sessions any day of the week, Monday through Sunday, between 13:00 and 24:00, though a ¥500 surcharge applies for sessions starting in the morning or after 21:30.<br />
        Each private session is held with between 1 and 5 participants, and fees are handled through a ticket system.<br />
        Sessions run 30–90 minutes, with each private lesson costing ¥2,000–4,000.
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Venue</h2>
      <p>
        <a
          href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/〒003-0021+北海道札幌市白石区栄通２丁目１−２７/@43.0409785,141.3938016,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x5f0b2bb4690b9e5f:0x622b301003410409!8m2!3d43.0409785!4d141.3959903"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          >2-1-27 Sakaedori, Shiroishi-ku, Sapporo (along Tohoku-dori) — Seishinkan Headquarters Dojo</a
        ><br />
        About 9 min (750m) on foot from Shiroishi Subway Station, about 18 min (1.4km) on foot from Tsukisamu-Chuo Subway Station, or about 4 min on foot from the "Sakaedori 1-chome" Chuo Bus stop
      </p>
      <div class="detail-gallery">
        <figure>
          <img
            src="/assets/images/about/honbu.jpg"
            alt="Seishinkan Headquarters Dojo"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
      <p>For more details, we hold information sessions at the Headquarters upon request. A trial private lesson (¥500) is also available.</p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Fees for Private Instruction Members</h2>
      <p>
        ◆ Enrollment fee ¥7,000<br />
        ◆ Annual fee ¥6,000 (includes insurance, etc./per fiscal year)<br />
        ◆ Karate gi ¥9,000~ (excl. tax)<br />
        ◆ Monthly fee ¥1,500 (membership registration fee)
      </p>

      <h2 class="detail-page__heading">Instructors</h2>
      <p>Classes are led by the Headquarters Shihan or an instructor.</p>

      <p class="detail-page__back">
        <a href="/en/dojo/">← Back to the Dojo & Class List</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
